    "# ── Cell 5: Multi-Source Dataset Acquisition ─────────────────────────────────\n",
    "#\n",
    "# Dataset target: ~11 000 – 13 000 images (balanced speed vs. accuracy)\n",
    "#\n",
    "# CONFIRMED SOURCES:\n",
    "#   ✅ Roboflow: sneha-tndy8/non-invasive-anemia-detection — 253 conjunctiva\n",
